<HL>
   Mattel Net Doubled
   To $29.3 Million
   In Fourth Quarter
   ----
   By Rhonda L. Rundle
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/07/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A9B
</SO>
<CO>
   MAT
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
<IN>
